Personal data collection process
We collect and otherwise process your personal data in the following ways:
From you.
For example, we may process your personal data when you email us.
From third parties.
In some cases, we may receive personal data about you from third parties,
    such as analytics tools connected to the App or when you make purchases through third-party services.
Through automatic collection.
Our App may connect with tools that automatically collect personal data,
    for example, to ensure the App works correctly.
